    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. those are good foundational points. can you expand more on the 'rule of law' aspect? my students need to be able to argue why enforcement is a moral/legal obligation rather than just a practical one. how would they frame the idea that breaking immigration law undermines the whole social contract?",
