      "content": "that makes sense. my students will definitely use that. one more thing though—some of the more progressive kids on the team are arguing that these same 'rule of law' arguments are just used to justify harsh treatment and ignore the humanitarian side of things. can you help me prepare a rebuttal to the idea that stricter enforcement is inherently inhumane? they want to argue that the law shouldn't supersede human rights, so how can we counter that from the enforcement perspective?",
